Package: rixpress
Title: Build Reproducible Analytical Pipelines With Nix
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bruno", "Rodrigues", , "bruno@brodrigues.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simplifies the creation of reproducible analytical pipelines
    using the 'Nix' package manager as a build automation tool. Heavily inspired by
    the 'targets' package.
